<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.7.8">
<l>kaṇṭu koṇṭeṉ kaika ḷāra niṉṟirup pātaṅkaḷmē</l>
<l>leṇṭi caiyu muḷḷa pūkkoṇ ṭētti yukantukantu</l>
<l>toṇṭa rōṅkaḷ pāṭi yāṭac cūḻkaṭaṉ ñālattuḷḷē</l>
<l>vaṇṭu ḻāyiṉ kaṇṇi vēntē vantiṭa killāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>While, so that the hands of me who have seen for myself are full, taking the flowers</l>
<l>there are to your sacred feet, praising in all the eight directions, rejoicing [and] rejoicing</l>
<l>we servants sing [and] dance, in the worlds with the surrounding sea,</l>
<l>o king with a generous tulsi chaplet, won’t you be able to come?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
